<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>BCSO - Règlement</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            --gold: #eab308;
            --gold-glow: rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.2);
            --bg-dark: #05070b;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            background: var(--bg-dark);
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            color: #e2e8f0;
        }

        .bcso-page {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% -20%, #1e293b 0%, #05070b 80%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding-top: 60px;
        }

        .title-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff, var(--gold));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .premium-card {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.65);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            border-radius: 18px;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }

        .premium-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px var(--gold-glow);
            border-color: var(--gold);
        }

        .icon-circle {
            width: 55px;
            height: 55px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(234,179,8,0.1);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--gold);
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .badge-grave {
            background: rgba(220,38,38,0.12);
            border: 1px solid #dc2626;
            color: #f87171;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .step {
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .small-text {
            opacity: 0.75;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="bcso-page">
<div class="container">

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h1 class="display-3 title-gradient">BCSO</h1>
        <p class="text-uppercase" style="letter-spacing:4px;">Règlement Intérieur & Protocoles</p>
    </div>

    <!-- DEVISE -->
    <div class="premium-card p-5 text-center mb-5">
        <i class="fas fa-star text-warning fa-3x mb-3"></i>
        <h3 class="fw-bold">HONOR • INTEGRITY • SERVICE</h3>
        <p class="small-text mt-3 mx-auto" style="max-width:600px;">
            Le Blaine County Sheriff's Office agit avec discipline, respect et professionnalisme afin de protéger les citoyens.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- I HRP -->
    <h3 class="section-title mb-3">I. Règlement HRP</h3>

    <div class="row g-3 mb-5">

        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="premium-card p-4 h-100">
                <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i></div>
                <h5>Article 1 - Respect</h5>
                <p class="small-text">
                    Respect obligatoire envers tous les joueurs et staff. Insultes HRP, toxicité et discrimination interdites.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="premium-card p-4 h-100">
                <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i></div>
                <h5>Article 2 - Professionnalisme</h5>
                <p class="small-text">
                    Le BCSO est une faction sérieuse. Comportement mature obligatoire et respect de la hiérarchie.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="premium-card p-4 h-100">
                <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i></div>
                <h5>Article 3 - Activité</h5>
                <p class="small-text">
                    Présence obligatoire. Absences longues à signaler sous peine de sanctions internes.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="premium-card p-4 h-100">
                <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-lock"></i></div>
                <h5>Article 4 - Confidentialité</h5>
                <p class="small-text">
                    Toutes les informations internes sont strictement confidentielles.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="premium-card p-4 h-100">
                <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-car"></i></div>
                <h5>Article 5 - Véhicules</h5>
                <p class="small-text">
                    Usage strictement professionnel. Drift et conduite irréaliste interdits.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="premium-card p-4 h-100">
                <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-gavel"></i></div>
                <h5>Article 6 - Sanctions</h5>
                <p class="small-text">
                    Avertissement, blâme, suspension, rétrogradation ou exclusion.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <!-- II RP -->
    <h3 class="section-title mb-3">II. Règlement RP</h3>

    <div class="premium-card p-4 mb-4">
        <h5>Article 1 - En service</h5>
        <p class="small-text">Uniforme obligatoire, radio active, respect hiérarchie.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="premium-card p-4 mb-4">
        <h5>Article 2 - Contrôle d’identité</h5>
        <p class="small-text">Justifié uniquement par situation RP valide.</p>
        <p class="small-text">✔ Routier ✔ Suspect ✔ Infraction ✔ Appel citoyen</p>
    </div>

    <div class="premium-card p-4 mb-4">
        <h5>Article 3 - Usage de la force</h5>

        <div class="step">Dialogue</div>
        <div class="step">Ordres verbaux</div>
        <div class="step">Menottage</div>
        <div class="step">Taser</div>
        <div class="step">Arme létale (dernier recours)</div>
    </div>

    <div class="premium-card p-4 mb-4">
        <h5>Article 4 - Armes</h5>
        <p class="small-text">Uniquement défense ou protection citoyenne.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="premium-card p-4 mb-4">
        <h5>Article 5 - Poursuites</h5>
        <p class="small-text">Communication radio obligatoire, conduite RP réaliste.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="premium-card p-4 mb-4">
        <h5>Article 6 - Fouille</h5>
        <p class="small-text">Toujours justifiée (arrestation, suspicion, danger).</p>
    </div>

    <div class="premium-card p-4 mb-4">
        <h5>Article 7 - Arrestation</h5>
        <div class="step">Lecture des droits</div>
        <div class="step">Menottage</div>
        <div class="step">Fouille</div>
        <div class="step">Inventaire</div>
        <div class="step">Rapport</div>
    </div>

    <div class="premium-card p-4 mb-4">
        <h5>Article 8 - Corruption</h5>
        <p class="small-text">Interdite sauf autorisation admin exceptionnelle.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="premium-card p-4 mb-4">
        <h5>Article 9 - Comportement</h5>
        <p class="small-text">Impartialité, sang-froid, respect des citoyens.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="premium-card p-4 mb-5">
        <h5>Article 10 - Radio</h5>
        <p class="small-text">Messages courts, clairs et professionnels.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAUTES GRAVES -->
    <h3 class="section-title mb-3">III. Fautes Graves</h3>

    <div class="premium-card p-4 mb-4">
        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="badge-grave">Abus de pouvoir</span>
            <span class="badge-grave">Free Arrest</span>
            <span class="badge-grave">Free Jail</span>
            <span class="badge-grave">Corruption</span>
            <span class="badge-grave">NoRP</span>
            <span class="badge-grave">Troll</span>
            <span class="badge-grave">Divulgation</span>
            <span class="badge-grave">Armes abusives</span>
        </div>

        <div class="alert alert-danger bg-opacity-10 mt-3">
            <strong>Tolérance zéro :</strong> exclusion immédiate possible.
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- DEVISE -->
    <div class="premium-card p-5 text-center mb-5">
        <h3 class="fw-bold">HONOR • INTEGRITY • SERVICE</h3>
        <p class="small-text mt-3">
            Le BCSO garantit un RP réaliste, sérieux et professionnel.
        </p>
    </div>

</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>